    title: 'Does adding solar raise property taxes?',
    h1: 'Property taxes and rooftop solar — what changes and what doesn\'t',
    description: 'Most U.S. states have property tax exemptions for residential solar, but the rules and the limits vary by state.',
    metaDescription: 'Do solar panels raise your property tax bill? Most states exempt residential solar — here is how to confirm yours does too.',
